"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"When in the public, it is advocated to behave politely, while still, some bad manners appear. The public place is for everybody to take the activities, as there are so many eyes watching, so we need to act politely and do not bring the bad influence to others. \\n 在公共场合，提倡举止文明，然而还是会有一些不良的行为出现。公共场所是给大家来活动的，由于有很多的眼睛在看着，因此我们最好举止文明，不要给别人带来不好的影响。 \\n The bad manners in the public are various. The most impolite manner is to throw away the rubbish. Some people are lazy to find the dustbin and choose the fastest way to get rid of their rubbish, they just throw away it. They don’t care whether it will do harm the environment and the people. How selfish he is. What’s more, some couples show their affection in front of the public, they kiss and touch each other, which embarrassed the public.   \\n 在公共场所的不良举行有很多。最不文明的行为就是乱扔垃圾。一些人懒于找垃圾桶，选择了最快摆脱垃圾的方式，他们直接把垃圾扔了。他们不在意是否会给环境和人来到害处。这是多么自私啊。而且，一些情侣在公共场合展示亲热的行为，他们彼此亲吻和触摸，这让大众感到尴尬。 \\n A public place is not suitable to show personal emotion, we need to behave ourselves. Imagine if someone is kissing in front of you, what you will do, you just can pretend not to see it, but in fact, you are awkward. Creating a harmonious environment needs everybody to work on it.  \\n 公众场合不适合展示个人情感，我们需要自我约束。想象一下，如果有人在你面前亲吻，你会怎么做，你只能装作没看到，但是实际上，你很尴尬。创造和谐的环境需要每个人的努力。\",\"timestamp\":1634967848,\"title\":\"The Bad Manners in the Public\"},\"digest\":\"3TB-dvNsho5VrjUGHU4wtYwwbGjAYabLpIVw8SEPsfE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xBD15a1827166fc0d5238bc7e1DeF2eBc88aa3f44\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"A52x22NcbtKtNG4eM-Um1bMgtUzR1X8xfbejFckgLnw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"UytGSiaAtWvqEWivNwIG-8bhAGrkv-EG4n9zh6wnpDo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"UXOyHmnRUxoRItCHiwLNS7w0QMRZh-fEqI0HP73JYncvGrf691VkoqdZ-Gd8AIh-wjOWLq3MavBWUP0v3ynmUw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdafa90f639f5ba9cd27566d876b9fb3a7231b5a4860a03bd77e0e095ad7684b724d44c9de9cb255f71bf6e321